<h1> Welcome to the Rock, Paper, Scissors game!</h1>

<h2> These are the game rules: </h2>

<p> The game is played with two players. You each have one chance to choose one of the following moves and enter it into the url: Rock, Paper or Scissor.</p>

<p>In the browser, the URL is:
  <b> http://localhost:4567/  </b>
</p>

<p>please enter:
  <b>    play / x /  y   </b>
  x = player 1 move
  y = player 2 move
</p>

  Rock loses to paper and wins to scissors, paper loses to scissors and wins to rock, and scissors lose to rock and win to paper.

  If both players choose the same signal, its a draw and try again!
</p>

<h2> Have fun! And may the best player win! </h2>

